[singing inside the television]
Pussy Kins Cat Food tastes real good. Satisfies cats like a cat food shuold. Hardens their muscles, softens their fur. Pussy Kins Cat Food makes them purr.
[the lady throws Sylvester out through the window, breaking it in the process, and he hits a tree with his head, the can of cat food then bounces off his head]
Are you getting more cat food lately, but enjoying it less?
